CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Acting on ester bonds;
            Phosphoric-diester hydrolases
SYSNAME     sphingomyelin ceramide-phosphohydrolase
REACTION    sphingomyelin + H2O = ceramide phosphate + choline [RN:R02542]
